================================================
BRANDING & DESIGN
================================================

STYLE NAME: Atlas Geometric Surrealism

COLORS:
- Broken Yellow: #E6A430
- Burnt Orange: #C94C1D
- Deep Bordeaux Red: #9E2B1E
- Teal Blue-Green: #1F5F5B
- Light Beige Background: #F9F4E7
RULE: Maintain 70/30 warm-to-cool color balance.

TYPOGRAPHY:
- Base font: A geometric serif-inspired typeface (preferably “Cormorant Garamond” or “Spectral” if web-safe).
- Clean geometric realism with surreal symbolic accents.

ICONOGRAPHY:
- Use Heroicons (outlined).
- Oji avatar: use local file “assets/Atlas_Logo.png”.
- No user avatar.

MOTIFS:
- Spirals, sun rays, organic curves, geometric horizons.
- Subtle paper grain texture overlay in background.

