================================================
DETAILED FUNCTIONALITY
================================================

CHAT INTERFACE (index.html):
- Large message window
- Message bubbles with timestamps
- AI messages use Atlas_Logo.png
- Smooth auto-scroll
- Animated “Oji is grabbing some binary coffee…” loader
- Input bar:
  * text field
  * file upload icon
  * send button
  * quick-actions dropdown
- Command bar triggered by “/”
- Modal: memory viewer
- Modal: chat history

SIDEBAR:
- Logo
- Navigation:
  * Chat
  * Dashboard
  * Project Panel
  * Settings
  * Admin
- Dark mode toggle
- Small surreal geometric accents

API.JS:
- Function sendMessage(text, files)
- POST to n8n webhook:
    headers: { "Content-Type": "application/json" }
- Return assistant response and append to chat.

